<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <!-- Open Graph data -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %>">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="http://www.sovacapital.com/" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.website_url %><%= require("../assets/images/fb_share.png") %>">
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.description %>">

  <!-- Twitter Card data -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %>">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.description %>">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.website_url %><%= require("../assets/images/twitter_share.png") %>">

  <!-- VK data -->
  <meta property="vk:title" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %>">
  <meta property="vk:description" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.description %>">
  <meta property="vk:url" content="http://www.sovacapital.com/">
  <meta property="vk:image" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.website_url %><%= require("../assets/images/vk_share.png") %>">

  <meta name="description" content="<%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.description %>">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="<%= require("../assets/images/favicon.png") %>" />

  <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
</head>
<body class="bg-ben">
<div class="d-md-flex flex-md-column">
  <header class="header flex justify-content-start">
    <a href="/"><img class="logo ml-2 ml-md-4" alt="sova logo" src=<%= require("../assets/images/logo.svg") %>></a>
  </header>

  <main class="content row px-md-5 mx-md-1">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-8 px-5 px-md-1 mt-md-5 pt-lg-5">
      <h1 class="title f-ult-light text-gray mb-4 mb-md-5 pb-md-3">terms of business</h1>

      <!-- START: Notification headline -->
      <h2 class="h3 headline f-semi-bold text-green my-3">Notification</h2>
      <!-- END: Notification headline -->

      <!-- START: Notifications -->
      <section>
        <div class="xsmall text-gray">20.03.2018</div>
        <div class="small f-semi-bold text-gray-dark mt-2 mb-3">
          Notification regarding changes to Terms of Business Updates on our New Company Name
        </div>
        <div class="small text-gray-dark f-light">
          <p>
            <span class="d-block f-semi-bold">Dear Client</span>
            Further to our recent communication regarding to changing of the company’s name from Otkritie Capital
            International Limited to Sova Capital Limited, please be informed that we have updated Terms of Business for
            Professional Clients version A (“Terms of Business A”), Terms of Business for Professional Clients version
            B, Terms of Business for Professional Clients version C on our website to reflect this change.
          </p>
          <p>
            Please note that all references to Otkritie Capital International Limited Terms of Business (A, B or C as
            applicable) in the Fees and Commission Schedule and other documents that have been executed between you and
            us in relation thereto, shall be deemed to be references to Sova Capital Limited Terms of Business for
            Professional Clients (A, B or C as applicable).
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any questions regarding change of name, please contact your Sales Representative or CRM or write
            to <a href="mailto:TOB_SCL@sovacapital.com">TOB_SCL@sovacapital.com</a> or call to
            <a href="tel:+442078268287">+44 207 826 82 87</a> (London direct number) or
            <a href="tel:+7 495 735 40 65">+7 495 735 40 65</a> (Moscow direct number), whichever is more convenient to
            you.
          </p>
          <p>
            The Terms of Business ("ToB") that will apply to transactions concluded between Sova Capital Limited and
            you, will be one of the followings, "Terms of Business A (4.0)" ("ToB A") or "Terms of Business B (4.0)"
            ("ToB B") "Terms of Business C (2.0)" ("ToB C"), depending on which services you would like to receive
            from Sova Capital Limited. Each ToB:
          </p>

          <ul class="list pl-3">
            <li><span class="text-gray-dark">relates to different services;</span></li>
            <li><span class="text-gray-dark">provides a different level of protection for your assets;</span></li>
            <li><span class="text-gray-dark">may include differing fees.</span></li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Copies of each version ToB A, ToB B and ToB C can be viewed below. Please contact us so we can advise you
            which ToB we would typically use for the specific services you require. For further details on the terms
            contained in the ToB, please see our FAQs and General Information sections of this website. If you have any
            questions at this stage, please contact us using the details provided in the Contact Details section.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- END: Notifications -->

      <!-- START: TOBs and FRs -->
      <section>
        <div class="section-title medium f-semi-bold text-green mb-3">Terms of Business</div>
        <ul class="small list pl-3">
          <li>
            <a class="text-gray-dark"
              href="http://www.otkritie-capital.com/common/img/uploaded/PDF-files1/osl/ToB_A-4.0-march.pdf"
              target="_blank">
              Terms of Business A (4.0)
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-gray-dark"
               href="http://www.otkritie-capital.com/common/img/uploaded/PDF-files1/osl/ToB_B-4.0-march.pdf"
               target="_blank">
              Terms of Business B (4.0)
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-gray-dark"
               href="http://www.otkritie-capital.com/common/img/uploaded/PDF-files1/osl/ToB_C-4.0-march-upd.pdf"
               target="_blank">
              Terms of Business C (2.0)
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <!-- END: TOBs and FRs -->
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer row px-4 px-md-5 mx-md-1">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 px-4 px-md-1 pb-2 pb-md-4 pt-5 pt-md-0">
      <a class="d-block text-gray small" href="http://www.otkritie-capital.com/en/tob/archive/" target="_blank">Archive</a>
      <a class="contact-email f-semi-bold small hovered" href="mailto:info@sovacapital.com">Email: info@sovacapital.com</a>
      <div class="disclaimer pt-2 pt-md-3">
        Unless specifically stated, this notice is for information purposes only and may not be
        considered as advice, is not an offer, recommendation or solicitation with respect to any transaction or an
        advertisement, nor is it an official confirmation of terms and does not form a fiduciary relationship.
        Additional information is available upon request.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <img class="image w-100 h-100 d-md-none" alt="ben" src=<%= require("../assets/images/ben.png") %>>
</div>
</body>
</html>
